-- Mylan gets FDA OK for generic of Colazal
-- 
-- Mon Dec 31, 2007 8:23am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/12/31/us-mylan-approval-idUSWNAS540520071231

 

 (Reuters) - Drug maker Mylan Inc MYL.N said its generic version of Salix Pharmaceuticals Ltd's ( SLXP.O ) Colazal capsules received final regulatory approval. 

 Mylan said Colazal capsules, which treats mild to moderate ulcerative colitis, had U.S. sales of about $130.9 million for the 12 months ending September 30. Mylan said in a statement its product will be shipped immediately. (Reporting by Shamik Paul in Bangalore)